              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "DMuTX",
                  "fill": "#1A1714",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "第三章　所有竞争都是失败的",
                  "lineHeight": 1.35,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 22,
                  "fontWeight": "700",
                  "letterSpacing": -0.3
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "dOkvM",
                  "fill": "#44403C",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "资本主义与竞争是对立的。资本主义建立在资本积累的基础之上，而在完全竞争的状态下，利润会被竞争消耗殆尽。然而，经济学家们的理论与商界领袖的实践之间存在根本性的矛盾。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.85,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "DdSon",
                  "name": "hl1",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#FEF3C7",
                  "cornerRadius": 6,
                  "stroke": {
                    "thickness": {
                      "left": 3
                    },
                    "fill": "#FCD34D"
                  },
                  "padding": [
                    10,
                    12
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "aVBUO",
                      "fill": "#78350F",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "如果你想创造并获取持久的价值，不要只是建立一个无差异的商品企业，要构建垄断。垄断企业可以负担得起思考长远利益的成本，而在竞争激烈的市场中生存的企业则不能。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.85,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "eehnl",
                  "fill": "#44403C",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "从谷歌的角度来看这个问题。谷歌的广告收入远高于其他所有搜索引擎的总和。这是因为谷歌在搜索领域建立了真正的垄断，而不是与必应、雅虎在边际差异上竞争。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.85,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "FMrnm",
                  "name": "hl2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#EFF6FF",
                  "cornerRadius": 6,
                  "stroke": {
                    "thickness": {
                      "left": 3
                    },
                    "fill": "#93C5FD"
                  },
                  "padding": [
                    10,
                    12
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "SKFlf",
                      "fill": "#1E40AF",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "垄断者可以通过把自己描述成在一个更大市场里竞争来隐藏自己的垄断地位；而处于激烈竞争中的企业则倾向于把自己描述为在一个小市场里的独一无二者。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.85,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "YCrT6",
                  "fill": "#44403C",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "创业者的任务不是模仿竞争者，而是避免竞争。这意味着要在一个利基市场占据主导地位，然后从那里扩展，而不是在现有的大市场中寻找一席之地。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.85,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
